<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-67-0302 </DOCNO><TEXT>An overview is given of INIS, the International Nuclear Information System,showing how the database can be used by practitioners and researchersin the field of nuclear medicine. An example is given of a typical onlinecomputer search of the INIS database and details of registration, costand access through the Australian Nuclear Science and Technology Organisation(ANSTO) are provided. INIS is one of the largest publicly available databasesin Australia.</TEXT></DOC>